```javascript
{
  data: [
    {
      id: string,
      slug: string,
      name: string,
      description: string,
      rule_type: 'event' | 'field' | 'threshold',
      category: 'demographic' | 'engagement' | 'behavior',
      conditions: object,
      points: number,
      max_per_day: number | null,
      max_per_lead: number | null,
      decay_days: number | null,
      priority: number,

      created_at: string,

}
```

```diff
+ /**

+ const StatsCard = ({ title, value, icon: Icon, color }) =&gt; (

+ /**
+  * Main Lead Scoring Page Component
+  */
+ const LeadScoringPage = () =&gt; {
+   // State
+   const [rules, setRules] = useState([]);
+   const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true);
+   const [error, setError] = useState(null);
+   const [page, setPage] = useState(0);
+   const [rowsPerPage, setRowsPerPage] = useState(10);
+   const [total, setTotal] = useState(0);
+   const [orderBy, setOrderBy] = useState('name');
+   const [order, setOrder] = useState('asc');
+   
+   // Filters
+   const [searchQuery, setSearchQuery] = useState('');
+   const [categoryFilter, setCategoryFilter] = useState('');
+   const [statusFilter, setStatusFilter] = useState('');
+   
+   // Dialog state
+   const [deleteDialogOpen, setDeleteDialogOpen] = useState(false);
+   const [ruleToDelete, setRuleToDelete] = useState(null);
+   const [deleteLoading, setDeleteLoading] = useState(false);
+   const [toggleLoading, setToggleLoading] = useState({});
+ 
+   /**
+    * Fetch scoring rules from API
+    */
+   const fetchRules = useCallback(async () =&gt; {
+     setLoading(true);
+     setError(null);
+     
+     try {
+       const params = {
+         page: page + 1,
+         limit: rowsPerPage,
+       };
+       
+       if (categoryFilter) {
+         params.category = categoryFilter;
+       }
+       if (statusFilter !== '') {
+         params.is_active = statusFilter === 'active';
+       }
+       
+       const response = await getScoringRules(params);
+       setRules(response.data || []);
+       setTotal(response.meta?.total || response.data?.length || 0);
+     } catch (err) {
+       console.error('Failed to fetch scoring rules:', err);
+       setError(err.message || 'Failed to load scoring rules');
+       setRules([]);
+     } finally {
+       setLoading(false);
+     }
+   }, [page, rowsPerPage, categoryFilter, statusFilter]);
+ 
+   useEffect(() =&gt; {
+     fetchRules();
+   }, [fetchRules]);
+ 
+   /**
+    * Handle sort change
+    */
+   const handleSort = (property) =&gt; {
+     const isAsc = orderBy === property &amp;&amp; order === 'asc';
+     setOrder(isAsc ? 'desc' : 'asc');
+     setOrderBy(property);
+   };
+ 
+   /**
+    * Handle page change
+    */
+   const handleChangePage = (event, newPage) =&gt; {
+     setPage(newPage);
+   };
+ 
+   /**
+    * Handle rows per page change
+    */
+   const handleChangeRowsPerPage = (event) =&gt; {
+     setRowsPerPage(parseInt(event.target.value, 10));
+     setPage(0);
+   };
+ 
+   /**
+    * Handle toggle active status
+    */
+   const handleToggleActive = async (rule) =&gt; {
+     setToggleLoading(prev =&gt; ({ ...prev, [rule.id]: true }));
+     
+     try {
+       await updateScoringRule(rule.id, { is_active: !rule.is_active });
+       // Update local state
+       setRules(prev =&gt; prev.map(r =&gt; 
+         r.id === rule.id ? { ...r, is_active: !r.is_active } : r
+       ));
+     } catch (err) {
+       console.error('Failed to toggle rule status:', err);
+       setError(&#96;Failed to update rule: ${err.message}&#96;);
+     } finally {
+       setToggleLoading(prev =&gt; ({ ...prev, [rule.id]: false }));
+     }
+   };
+ 
+   /**
+    * Handle delete click
+    */
+   const handleDeleteClick = (rule) =&gt; {
+     setRuleToDelete(rule);
+     setDeleteDialogOpen(true);
+   };
+ 
+   /**
+    * Handle delete confirm
+    */
+   const handleDeleteConfirm = async () =&gt; {
+     if (!ruleToDelete) return;
+     
+     setDeleteLoading(true);
+     
+     try {
+       await deleteScoringRule(ruleToDelete.id);
+       setDeleteDialogOpen(false);
+       setRuleToDelete(null);
+       // Refresh the list
+       fetchRules();
+     } catch (err) {
+       console.error('Failed to delete rule:', err);
+       setError(&#96;Failed to delete rule: ${err.message}&#96;);
+     } finally {
+       setDeleteLoading(false);
+     }
+   };
+ 
+   /**
+    * Handle delete cancel
+    */
+   const handleDeleteCancel = () =&gt; {
+     setDeleteDialogOpen(false);
+     setRuleToDelete(null);
+   };
+ 
+   /**
+    * Filter rules by search query (client-side)
+    */
+   const filteredRules = rules.filter(rule =&gt; {
+     if (!searchQuery) return true;
+     const query = searchQuery.toLowerCase();
+     return (
+       rule.name?.toLowerCase().includes(query) ||
+       rule.slug?.toLowerCase().includes(query) ||
+       rule.description?.toLowerCase().includes(query)
+     );
+   });
+ 
+   /**
+    * Sort rules (client-side)
+    */
+   const sortedRules = [...filteredRules].sort((a, b) =&gt; {
+     const aValue = a[orderBy] ?? '';
+     const bValue = b[orderBy] ?? '';
+     
+     if (typeof aValue === 'string') {
+       return order === 'asc' 
+         ? aValue.localeCompare(bValue)
+         : bValue.localeCompare(aValue);
+     }
+     
+     return order === 'asc' ? aValue - bValue : bValue - aValue;
+   });
+ 
+   // Calculate stats
+   const totalRules = total;
+   const activeRules = rules.filter(r =&gt; r.is_active).length;
+   const totalPoints = rules.reduce((sum, r) =&gt; sum + (r.points || 0), 0);
+ 
+   return (
+     &lt;Box sx={{ p: 3 }}&gt;
+       {/* Page Header */}
+       &lt;Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'flex-start', mb: 4 }}&gt;
+         &lt;Box&gt;
+           &lt;Typography variant="h4" sx={{ fontWeight: 300, display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 1.5 }}&gt;
+             &lt;ScoringIcon sx={{ color: 'primary.main' }} /&gt;
+             Lead Scoring Rules
+           &lt;/Typography&gt;
+           &lt;Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" sx={{ mt: 0.5 }}&gt;
+             Configure scoring rules to automatically qualify leads
+           &lt;/Typography&gt;
+         &lt;/Box&gt;
+         &lt;Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 1 }}&gt;
+           &lt;Tooltip title="Refresh"&gt;
+             &lt;IconButton onClick={fetchRules} disabled={loading}&gt;
+               &lt;RefreshIcon /&gt;
+             &lt;/IconButton&gt;
+           &lt;/Tooltip&gt;
+           &lt;Button
+             variant="contained"
+             startIcon={&lt;AddIcon /&gt;}
+             disabled
+             sx={{ opacity: 0.6 }}
+           &gt;
+             Create Rule
+           &lt;/Button&gt;
+         &lt;/Box&gt;
+       &lt;/Box&gt;
+ 
+       {/* Stats Cards */}
+       &lt;Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 2, mb: 3, flexWrap: 'wrap' }}&gt;
+         &lt;StatsCard 
+           title="Total Rules" 
+           value={loading ? '—' : totalRules} 
+           icon={ScoringIcon} 
+           color="#4A90A4" 
+         /&gt;
+         &lt;StatsCard 
+           title="Active Rules" 
+           value={loading ? '—' : activeRules} 
+           icon={CategoryIcon} 
+           color="#28A745" 
+         /&gt;
+         &lt;StatsCard 
+           title="Avg Points" 
+           value={loading || rules.length === 0 ? '—' : Math.round(totalPoints / rules.length)} 
+           icon={PointsIcon} 
+           color="#6C5CE7" 
+         /&gt;
+       &lt;/Box&gt;
+ 
+       {/* Error Alert */}
+       {error &amp;&amp; (
+         &lt;Alert severity="error" sx={{ mb: 3 }} onClose={() =&gt; setError(null)}&gt;
+           {error}
+         &lt;/Alert&gt;
+       )}
+ 
+       {/* Filters */}
+       &lt;Card sx={{ mb: 3 }}&gt;
+         &lt;CardContent sx={{ py: 2, '&amp;:last-child': { pb: 2 } }}&gt;
+           &lt;Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 2, flexWrap: 'wrap', alignItems: 'center' }}&gt;
+             &lt;TextField
+               placeholder="Search rules..."
+               size="small"
+               value={searchQuery}
+               onChange={(e) =&gt; setSearchQuery(e.target.value)}
+               InputProps={{
+                 startAdornment: (
+                   &lt;InputAdornment position="start"&gt;

+               select
+               label="Status"
+               size="small"
+               value={statusFilter}
+               onChange={(e) =&gt; {
+                 setStatusFilter(e.target.value);
+                 setPage(0);
+               }}
+               sx={{ minWidth: 130 }}
+             &gt;
+               &lt;MenuItem value=""&gt;All Status&lt;/MenuItem&gt;
+               &lt;MenuItem value="active"&gt;Active&lt;/MenuItem&gt;
+               &lt;MenuItem value="inactive"&gt;Inactive&lt;/MenuItem&gt;
+             &lt;/TextField&gt;
+             {(categoryFilter || statusFilter || searchQuery) &amp;&amp; (
+               &lt;Button
+                 size="small"
+                 onClick={() =&gt; {
+                   setCategoryFilter('');
+                   setStatusFilter('');
+                   setSearchQuery('');
+                   setPage(0);
+                 }}
+               &gt;
+                 Clear Filters
+               &lt;/Button&gt;
+             )}
+           &lt;/Box&gt;
+         &lt;/CardContent&gt;
+       &lt;/Card&gt;
+ 
+       {/* Rules Table */}
+       &lt;Card&gt;
+         &lt;TableContainer component={Paper} sx={{ bgcolor: 'background.paper' }}&gt;
+           &lt;Table&gt;
+             &lt;TableHead&gt;
+               &lt;TableRow&gt;
+                 &lt;TableCell&gt;
+                   &lt;TableSortLabel
+                     active={orderBy === 'name'}
+                     direction={orderBy === 'name' ? order : 'asc'}
+                     onClick={() =&gt; handleSort('name')}
+                   &gt;
+                     Rule Name
+                   &lt;/TableSortLabel&gt;
+                 &lt;/TableCell&gt;
+                 &lt;TableCell&gt;
+                   &lt;TableSortLabel
+                     active={orderBy === 'category'}
+                     direction={orderBy === 'category' ? order : 'asc'}
+                     onClick={() =&gt; handleSort('category')}
+                   &gt;
+                     Category
+                   &lt;/TableSortLabel&gt;
+                 &lt;/TableCell&gt;
+                 &lt;TableCell&gt;Type&lt;/TableCell&gt;
+                 &lt;TableCell align="right"&gt;
+                   &lt;TableSortLabel
+                     active={orderBy === 'points'}
+                     direction={orderBy === 'points' ? order : 'asc'}
+                     onClick={() =&gt; handleSort('points')}
+                   &gt;
+                     Points
+                   &lt;/TableSortLabel&gt;
+                 &lt;/TableCell&gt;
+                 &lt;TableCell&gt;Limits&lt;/TableCell&gt;
+                 &lt;TableCell align="center"&gt;Status&lt;/TableCell&gt;
+                 &lt;TableCell align="right"&gt;Actions&lt;/TableCell&gt;
+               &lt;/TableRow&gt;
+             &lt;/TableHead&gt;
+             &lt;TableBody&gt;
+               {loading ? (
+                 &lt;TableSkeleton rows={rowsPerPage} /&gt;
+               ) : sortedRules.length === 0 ? (
+                 &lt;TableRow&gt;
+                   &lt;TableCell colSpan={7} align="center" sx={{ py: 8 }}&gt;
+                     &lt;Typography color="text.secondary"&gt;
+                       {searchQuery || categoryFilter || statusFilter 
+                         ? 'No rules match your filters' 
+                         : 'No scoring rules found'}
+                     &lt;/Typography&gt;
+                   &lt;/TableCell&gt;
+                 &lt;/TableRow&gt;
+               ) : (
+                 sortedRules.map((rule) =&gt; (
+                   &lt;TableRow
+                     key={rule.id}
+                     hover
+                     sx={{
+                       '&amp;:hover': { bgcolor: 'action.hover' },
+                       opacity: rule.is_active ? 1 : 0.6,
+                     }}
+                   &gt;
+                     &lt;TableCell&gt;
+                       &lt;Box&gt;
+                         &lt;Typography variant="body2" fontWeight={500}&gt;
+                           {rule.name}
+                         &lt;/Typography&gt;
+                         &lt;Typography variant="caption" color="text.secondary"&gt;
+                           {rule.slug}
+                         &lt;/Typography&gt;
+                       &lt;/Box&gt;
+                     &lt;/TableCell&gt;
+                     &lt;TableCell&gt;
+                       &lt;CategoryBadge category={rule.category} /&gt;
+                     &lt;/TableCell&gt;
+                     &lt;TableCell&gt;
+                       &lt;RuleTypeBadge ruleType={rule.rule_type} /&gt;
+                     &lt;/TableCell&gt;
+                     &lt;TableCell align="right"&gt;
+                       &lt;PointsDisplay points={rule.points} /&gt;
+                     &lt;/TableCell&gt;
+                     &lt;TableCell&gt;
+                       &lt;LimitsDisplay 
+                         maxPerDay={rule.max_per_day} 
+                         maxPerLead={rule.max_per_lead} 
+                       /&gt;
+                     &lt;/TableCell&gt;
+                     &lt;TableCell align="center"&gt;
+                       &lt;Tooltip title={rule.is_active ? 'Click to deactivate' : 'Click to activate'}&gt;
+                         &lt;span&gt;
+                           &lt;Switch
+                             checked={rule.is_active}
+                             onChange={() =&gt; handleToggleActive(rule)}
+                             disabled={toggleLoading[rule.id]}
+                             size="small"
+                             color="success"
+                           /&gt;
+                         &lt;/span&gt;
+                       &lt;/Tooltip&gt;
+                     &lt;/TableCell&gt;
+                     &lt;TableCell align="right"&gt;
+                       &lt;Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'flex-end', gap: 0.5 }}&gt;
+                         &lt;Tooltip title="Edit (Coming soon)"&gt;
+                           &lt;span&gt;
+                             &lt;IconButton size="small" disabled&gt;
+                               &lt;EditIcon fontSize="small" /&gt;
+                             &lt;/IconButton&gt;
+                           &lt;/span&gt;
+                         &lt;/Tooltip&gt;
+                         &lt;Tooltip title="Delete"&gt;
+                           &lt;IconButton 
+                             size="small" 
+                             onClick={() =&gt; handleDeleteClick(rule)}
+                             color="error"
+                           &gt;
+                             &lt;DeleteIcon fontSize="small" /&gt;
+                           &lt;/IconButton&gt;
+                         &lt;/Tooltip&gt;
+                       &lt;/Box&gt;
+                     &lt;/TableCell&gt;
+                   &lt;/TableRow&gt;
+                 ))
+               )}
+             &lt;/TableBody&gt;
+           &lt;/Table&gt;
+         &lt;/TableContainer&gt;
+         &lt;TablePagination
+           component="div"
+           count={total}
+           page={page}
+           onPageChange={handleChangePage}
+           rowsPerPage={rowsPerPage}
+           onRowsPerPageChange={handleChangeRowsPerPage}
+           rowsPerPageOptions={[5, 10, 25, 50]}
+         /&gt;
+       &lt;/Card&gt;
+ 
+       {/* Delete Confirmation Dialog */}
+       &lt;DeleteDialog
+         open={deleteDialogOpen}
+         rule={ruleToDelete}
+         onClose={handleDeleteCancel}
+         onConfirm={handleDeleteConfirm}
+         loading={deleteLoading}
+       /&gt;
+     &lt;/Box&gt;
+   );
+ };
+ 
+ export default LeadScoringPage;
+ 
```

   - Vollständige Scoring Rules List Page mit DataGrid

   - Sortierbare Spalten (Name, Category, Points)

### Features der Page:

| Feature | Implementierung |
|---------|-----------------|
| **DataGrid** | MUI Table mit Spalten: Rule Name, Category, Type, Points, Limits, Status, Actions |
| **Filter** | Dropdown für Category (demographic/engagement/behavior) und Status (active/inactive) |
| **Suche** | Client-seitige Suche nach Name, Slug, Description |
| **Sortierung** | Klickbare Spaltenheader für Name, Category, Points |
| **Actions** | Enable/Disable Toggle, Edit (disabled), Delete mit Bestätigung |
| **Pagination** | MUI TablePagination mit 5/10/25/50 Rows per Page |
| **Stats** | Cards mit Total Rules, Active Rules, Avg Points |
| **Error Handling** | Alert-Komponente für API-Fehler |

Die Seite funktioniert mit der bestehenden DataProvider API (`getScoringRules`, `updateScoringRule`, `deleteScoringRule`) und ist vollständig in die Navigation integriert.
